{"tid":519311,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"平讓全新未開封foreo luna2","createTime":"2018-01-04T08:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T22:04:31.000Z","uid":158840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a962961beb00bbcfa52edbcff202873fcea05a","tid":519311,"uid":158840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:24:07.000Z","msg":"本身想買俾呀妹做聖誕禮物<br />\n點知佢自己買咗另一個牌子唔鍾意呢部<br />\n我自己已經用緊同一部<br />\n依家多咗部出嚟想平讓俾巴絲們<br />\nLuna2係新版嚟 背面有舒緩模式用嚟按摩既<br />\n呢部係俾敏感肌既 紫色<br />\n可以參考官網介紹<a href=\"https://www.foreo.com/luna-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreo.com%2Fluna-2&d=JSzv5puKCyEP%2Bw%2Ffh5mnCcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3edd4d85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foreo.com/luna-2</a><br />\n<br />\n價錢可議 打算原價八折出 只求售出<br />\n一定平過友和同官網<br />\n<br />\n啱啱12月至喺官網買 <br />\n可以自己上官網登記番2年同10年既保養<br />\n淨係開咗順豐袋<br />\n可提供單據作購買證明<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可tg <a href=\"https://t.me/laurep\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flaurep&d=JSzv5puKCyEP%2Bw%2Ffh5mnCcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9dfc1adb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/laurep</a><br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n圖係我自己用緊嗰部 一模一樣既<br />\n出呢部淨係開咗順豐袋冇嘢可以影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/161846_793e3a5ba7b77d68efe2c348c4e9d498.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F161846_793e3a5ba7b77d68efe2c348c4e9d498.png&h=4e17bfc1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/161847_af766134f4a7402d38063648c7c59663.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F161847_af766134f4a7402d38063648c7c59663.png&h=7fcc06e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/161848_7665965fdbb528c539c90d9c1b97cb51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F161848_7665965fdbb528c539c90d9c1b97cb51.png&h=277645f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/04/161849_c21047c9ee2f9b1ea9eedfb5f45d34ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2F161849_c21047c9ee2f9b1ea9eedfb5f45d34ec.png&h=02a94c5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d96cbf42bf1e763cb5c831b10cd7680afffb380e","tid":519311,"uid":87163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"$200"},{"pid":"dafda106faa6e0599c377cfdf8767bac7df30efb","tid":519311,"uid":158840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"已賣 謝謝"},{"pid":"a87c62120d1611b49a6bde0e07b653740ec620a7","tid":519311,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T22:04:31.000Z","msg":"其實喱啲機好唔好用？<br />\n朋友送左部比我<br />\n有用緊<br />\n但應該唔係咩大牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當佢係彷製品啦<br />\n想問有無分別"}]}